docs.snippet: Critical financial and political conditions in France and Spain made for an irregular trend in foreign exchange values last week. The French franc hovered around its low for the year, at 6.58 1/4 cents, bringing in its wake fresh engagements of gold...
docs.lead_paragraph: Critical financial and political conditions in France and Spain made for an irregular trend in foreign exchange values last week. The French franc hovered around its low for the year, at 6.58 1/4 cents, bringing in its wake fresh engagements of gold in Paris, while the Madrid unit slumped to a new low for the year at 11.92 cents.
